ZH: 我去了医院，他住在病房里。
EN: I went to the hospital, and he stayed in the ward.

ZH: 我昨天探望了她在病房的祖父。
EN: I visited her grandfather in the hospital ward yesterday.

ZH: 我的朋友在病房里住了一个星期。
EN: My friend stayed in the hospital ward for a week.

ZH: 医生告诉我，他的病情已经转移到了病房。
EN: The doctor told me that his condition has been moved to the ward.

ZH: 我今天帮忙搬运了一些物品到医院的病房。
EN: I helped to move some items to the hospital ward today.

ZH: 病房里的设施很干净整洁。
EN: The facilities in the ward are very clean and tidy.

ZH: 我希望他能尽快康复，出院离开病房。
EN: I hope he can recover soon and leave the ward.

ZH: 病房里的护士非常照顾病人。
EN: The nurses in the ward take very good care of the patients.

ZH: 她在病房里度过了一段不愉快的时间。
EN: She spent an unpleasant time in the ward.

ZH: 病房里的气氛非常压抑。
EN: The atmosphere in the ward is very depressing.

ZH: 我在病房里见到了一位认识的病人。
EN: I saw a familiar patient in the ward.

ZH: 明天我会去看望我的家人在病房里。
EN: I will visit my family in the ward tomorrow.

ZH: 病房里的医疗设备很先进。
EN: The medical equipment in the ward is very advanced.

ZH: 她需要长时间在病房里接受治疗。
EN: She needs to be treated in the ward for a long time.

ZH: 我今天给病房里的患者们送去了一些水果。
EN: I brought some fruits to the patients in the ward today.

ZH: 他在病房里度过了一个难忘的生日。
EN: He spent a memorable birthday in the ward.

ZH: 病房里的窗户可以看到美丽的风景。
EN: The windows in the ward offer a view of beautiful scenery.

ZH: 我希望他尽快康复，不再需要待在病房里。
EN: I hope he can recover soon and no longer need to stay in the ward.

ZH: 病房里的空气清新，让人感觉舒适。
EN: The air in the ward is fresh and comfortable.

ZH: 我们每天都会向病房里的病人们送去一些关心和问候。
EN: Every day, we send care and greetings to the patients in the ward.
